    public class FencedAkkaRpcActor<F extends java.io.Serializable,T extends FencedRpcEndpoint<F> & RpcGateway>
extends AkkaRpcActor<T>
    Fenced extension of the AkkaRpcActor. This actor will be started for FencedRpcEndpoint and is responsible for filtering out invalid messages with respect to the current fencing token.
